aboutpara: Hi my name is Daniela Mansolino.I am passionate about communication, learning and coding. My journalism background cultivated effective communication. Seeking new opportunities I moved to the United States five years ago where I developed adaptability. My curiosity guided my professional path to software engineering and my dedication led me to the completion of a Software Engineering program at General Assembly, where I honed my expertise. Now, my sights are set on a career as a full-stack developer. .
